	ZeRoN_WoW is a World of Warcraft Website.

	For further information on the ZeRoN_WoW project, please visit the
	project website at http://zeron-wow.dyndns.org/

	SQL files to create the database can be found in the sql directory. Files
	to update your database from an older revision/version can be found in the
	sql/updates directory.

	See http://zeron-wow.dyndns.org/ for installation instructions on Windows.
	This is an apache Working Website, also works on Linux.

	Our Bug Tracker is located here.
